{"tid":2488267,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳陳奕迅有意出席ViuTV音樂頒獎典禮  TVB聯絡後拒絕邀請","createTime":"2021-04-14T06:27:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T06:45:02.000Z","uid":358086,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d22cdfa5b0b7349dbcfebefa77f08ea75d603227","tid":2488267,"uid":358086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T06:27:36.000Z","msg":"ViuTV將於周日（4月18日）舉行該台首個舉辦的大型音樂頒獎典禮《Chill Club推介榜年度推介20/21》，當晚正好與TVB重頭直播節目《開心大綜藝》硬碰。<br />\n<br />\n兩台電視大戰，近日有傳TVB於本周日為應付《Chill Club推介榜年度推介20/21》，有意延長《開心大綜藝》的播出時間，由原本的1小時改為2小時，正面迎戰ViuTV。<br />\n<br />\n不過作為節目主持之一的阿Bob林盛斌回覆傳媒指，暫未收到公司指示。即是延長《開心大綜藝》只屬傳聞，未必是真。<br />\n<br />\n早前，有傳陳奕迅有意出席ViuTV於周日舉行的《Chill Club推介榜年度推介20/21》，TVB得知後即聯絡陳奕迅，希望他為首集《開心大綜藝》任嘉賓，不過之後陳奕迅方面表示為平等對待，已拒絕了兩台的邀請。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXbxivYjfXFAtA3ekjCW9M45E7s2piHHqSxxiRQr3C2E4?filename=QFbgqh4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQFbgqh4.png&h=cd7e39ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2931400/?r=mcsdfb&amp;fbclid=IwAR2iKOtHb4cqn3gbmButUzF4l1-0tW949yGkr-lI7dVGtCe7kgOubSGf9H0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2931400%2F%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb%26fbclid%3DIwAR2iKOtHb4cqn3gbmButUzF4l1-0tW949yGkr-lI7dVGtCe7kgOubSGf9H0&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvpszS%2Fgy1fqSqMk7TcT3QhU%3D&h=467d5bf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2931400/?r=mcsdfb&amp;fbclid=IwAR2iKOtHb4cqn3gbmButUzF4l1-0tW949yGkr-lI7dVGtCe7kgOubSGf9H0</a>"},{"pid":"fe4150b0b6138aed5e3d1336314c77d8979d0ff5","tid":2488267,"uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T06:40:08.000Z","msg":"兩個台都俾唔夠錢"},{"pid":"e03d16c1b05d01f603d630826c0b8481f081a5d3","tid":2488267,"uid":51200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T06:43:44.000Z","msg":"單春做咗咁多年，梗係知道tbb d On9野<br />\n乜都大哂<br />\n但香港啲所謂明星都係世界仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" 